title: WTB: T206 Working on Set Need Low to Mid Grade
author: chris

posts.post_title: WTB: T206 Working on Set Need Low to Mid Grade
posts.post_content:
Hello - I am working on the T206 set and am looking for groups of cards to get going. I will take duplicates of cards I already own as I can trade them for cards I need. I am looking for any condition Poor to EX, graded or raw. Please email me at [url]bucklercards@yahoo.com[/url] with any for sale. I will pay very reasonable. I will also trade for large groups of cards. 

Thanks,
Chris :)
Chris,  do you prefer more interesting backs?  I ask because they cost a little more, but I have quite a few that I haven't listed yet.
